  "local_port": 36914,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Is there any good institute for differently abled child near Noida areas?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several institutes and centers near the Noida area that cater to the needs of differently-abled children, providing education, therapy, and support. Here are a few notable ones:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Manovikas Charitable Society**\n   - **Location**: Sector 12, Noida\n   - **Services**: Special education, vocational training, therapy (speech, occupational), and rehabilitation for children with intellectual and developmental disabilities.\n   - **Website**: [Manovikas Charitable Society](https://www.manovikas.co.in/)\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Amaze Charitable Trust**\n   - **Location**: Sector 44, Noida\n   - **Services**: Educational programs, speech therapy, occupational therapy, and counseling for children with autism and other developmental disorders.\n   - **Website**: [Amaze Charitable Trust](https://www.amazecare.org/)\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Tamana Special School**\n   - **Location**: Near Delhi-Noida border\n   - **Services**: Special education, therapy, and vocational training for children with autism, intellectual disabilities, and multiple disabilities.\n   - **Website**: [Tamana](https://www.tamana.org/)\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Sparsh for Children**\n   - **Location**: Sector 44, Noida\n   - **Services**: Special education, early intervention, and therapy for children with autism, ADHD, and other learning disabilities.\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Asha Kiran Special Needs School**\n   - **Location**: Sector 53, Noida\n   - **Services**: Comprehensive programs for children with intellectual and developmental disabilities, including special education and therapy.\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Delta Learning Center**\n   - **Location**: Nearby Noida (Greater Noida/West)\n   - **Services**: Special education and therapy for children with autism, ADHD, and learning disabilities.\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Kiran Society for Inclusive Education**\n   - **Location**: Noida\n   - **Services**: Inclusive education, therapy, and vocational training for children with disabilities.\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Ummeed Child Development Center**\n   - **Location**: Multiple centers near Noida\n   - **Services**: Comprehensive care for children with developmental disabilities, including autism, cerebral palsy, and learning disorders.\n\n---\n\nIt's advisable to visit or contact these institutes directly to understand their programs, facilities, and whether they meet your child's specific needs. Most of these centers also provide counseling and guidance for parents.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
